data.description: Newer single story Lennar NextGen smart home has been priced to sell!!  Providing great curb appeal, brick accents on the facade, low maintenance desert front landscaping and just a few steps from the Valencia Heights community park and green belt. Newer home was built in 2016 and is being sold by the original owners.  Fantastic open kitchen/living layout with a gas stove, black granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, pantry and tall 42” upper maple cabinets with crown molding.  Kitchen floor plan is open to the family room area with plenty of natural light. Formal dining room and living room.  Upgrades include surround sound wiring, security system, programmable thermostat, 12x24 tile flooring, recessed lighting, ceiling fans throughout and 9ft ceilings.  All appliances are included. Relax and enjoy your fully landscaped low maintenance backyard with fruit trees.  Small community with only 52 homes and no thru streets. Nestled in a very quiet neighborhood of Mesa with a private community gate to the canal trail for walking/biking.  Conveniently located near the 60 &202 freeways, Banner Gateway Medical Center, several parks, and Dana Park Village Square featuring AJ’s, great restaurants, entertainment and shopping.  Prime central location is excellent for commuting.  Don’t miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
